name: v2.5.5.3
body:
### Stable version
- **End to end encryption support:** Now the API is able to encrypt and decrypt messages automatically
- Update ver. to 2.13.9 (Nokia data)
- Applied receipt fix #1093
- Applied network fixes #1027 
- Improved API structure, now its more organized
- New logger system added
- Moved registration functions to a new different class
- Moved to GPLv3+ license
- Added compatibility fix

and lots of improvements and fixes (more than 150 commits!)

**Note:** For encryption support, check [dependencies](https://github.com/WHAnonymous/Chat-API/wiki/Dependencies)

name: v2.5.2
body:
**Stable version**
- `reconnect()` function added
- If it doesn't get any data in 5 minutes it will close connection, you can use `reconnect` to stablish a connection again. #870
